{"tid":122370,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"沖繩北部到中部有乜玩？","createTime":"2017-02-16T03:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T15:30:14.000Z","uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae276a99fec5b789d28936bc9090ae635a4f4346","tid":122370,"uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:06:32.000Z","msg":"三月頭去沖繩<br />\n<br />\n第二日去水族館+住隔離<br />\n第三晚住美國村<br />\n<br />\n中間有乜好做？<br />\n會同老人家去，希望唔太激又大家啱玩嘅"},{"pid":"d09da51003836e7a86cd3addb3eb68ff94646fc7","tid":122370,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"766f5658ff520d3c4b089e525094b323ef42134e","tid":122370,"uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>萬座毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩到幾耐？<br />\n係咪都係睇下個象鼻睇下海？"},{"pid":"b21c2cc10aebd5e1bd5540e47ae7c56adecd5bc5","tid":122370,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>萬座毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩到幾耐？<br />\n係咪都係睇下個象鼻睇下海？</blockquote><br />\n其實你如果唔係會慢慢喺嗰度hea嘅話，基本上影下相就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自駕遊可以喺北部落緊中部途中去一去"},{"pid":"123e9bd3e800b08e45fa8bfcff2f1c0fda89b5ea","tid":122370,"uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>萬座毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩到幾耐？<br />\n係咪都係睇下個象鼻睇下海？</blockquote><br />\n其實你如果唔係會慢慢喺嗰度hea嘅話，基本上影下相就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自駕遊可以喺北部落緊中部途中去一去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美國村預幾多時間好？<br />\n多唔多嘢買？<br />\n成團好多女人，我怕太少時間買嘢會俾人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6dbb762fcfd724a747ef0fa492476783c3b30f","tid":122370,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>萬座毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩到幾耐？<br />\n係咪都係睇下個象鼻睇下海？</blockquote><br />\n其實你如果唔係會慢慢喺嗰度hea嘅話，基本上影下相就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自駕遊可以喺北部落緊中部途中去一去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美國村預幾多時間好？<br />\n多唔多嘢買？<br />\n成團好多女人，我怕太少時間買嘢會俾人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沖繩嚟講，我覺得<br />\n美國村已經叫做多嘢買<br />\n一係naha 一係美國村"},{"pid":"01ef1e0da35d82fcb0bc6ac6100e90b750b291ee","tid":122370,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>萬座毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩到幾耐？<br />\n係咪都係睇下個象鼻睇下海？</blockquote><br />\n其實你如果唔係會慢慢喺嗰度hea嘅話，基本上影下相就完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自駕遊可以喺北部落緊中部途中去一去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快則十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜Q 都冇 得條J 俾你影吓相<br />\n影相位得嗰個standard 位置"},{"pid":"96d0409752c69666cfbe08e3c91ffd5440280b39","tid":122370,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"殘波岬<br />\n<br />\n萬座毛<br />\n<br />\n海中展望塔<br />\n<br />\n菠蘿園<br />\n<br />\n美麗海水族館<br />\n<br />\n古宇利島/塔<br />\n<br />\nAeon Mall [url][/url]"},{"pid":"e7cfcb040775e898de4def406c7ce87db7ef7bee","tid":122370,"uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殘波岬<br />\n<br />\n萬座毛<br />\n<br />\n海中展望塔<br />\n<br />\n菠蘿園<br />\n<br />\n美麗海水族館<br />\n<br />\n古宇利島/塔<br />\n<br />\nAeon Mall </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲乜柒城遺址值唔值得去？<br />\n係好流好小型嗰啲？"},{"pid":"840520e63b530c6578266bbd6d7d6f01104ee446","tid":122370,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>殘波岬<br />\n<br />\n萬座毛<br />\n<br />\n海中展望塔<br />\n<br />\n菠蘿園<br />\n<br />\n美麗海水族館<br />\n<br />\n古宇利島/塔<br />\n<br />\nAeon Mall </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗰啲乜柒城遺址值唔值得去？<br />\n係好流好小型嗰啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去過今歸仁遺跡，講真，都係好流下，得啲爛石牆同石碑<br />\n<br />\n老人家去都應該幾悶下。<br />\n<br />\n殘坡岬同海中展望塔都ok，個人覺得好過萬座毛添。"},{"pid":"6416614ddf4d7d747b771048a3ac0739e3907d77","tid":122370,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"如果你住中部果陣<br />\n<br />\n可以去琉球村，啲老人家應該會 buy。"},{"pid":"1e7e6035ea943114f479e407beb37011ceb050e7","tid":122370,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"同問：我3月頭都去，租車自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c5a3535f55a1d08cfc975132b841ba8ada06b4","tid":122370,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"「LIHKG 原創」2016 沖繩自駕遊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/37131/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/37131/page/1?ref=web</a>"},{"pid":"5af14482ae741295468289aeeb27be4b63eb873b","tid":122370,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「LIHKG 原創」2016 沖繩自駕遊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/37131/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/37131/page/1?ref=web</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/37131/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/37131/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf2fc7b95c95341c07510e430b46d9773c7905e","tid":122370,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"水族館可以玩大半日<br />\n萬座毛玩10分鐘<br />\n美國村得餐廳鋪頭，冇咩特別<br />\n殘波岬睇風景影下相可以行個零鐘嘅"},{"pid":"63062fb84c4c8b656ea28fc45333d54515fe10f9","tid":122370,"uid":75520,"like":0,"dislike":