g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2810ddfbb4dda54b0f45c9c748889eb406cb261","tid":122370,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:45:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沖繩唔自駕遊真係差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識渣車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n7個人去，班友想租10座hiace 但得我有大巴牌（國際D牌）<br />\n<br />\n最後決定租2部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebab6cff3f7d5d90629fd17b9cdc4947de08041","tid":122370,"uid":39084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"萬座毛可以玩個幾鐘，其中一個鐘攞黎排隊"}]}